{"tid":1468177,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣]應付屈手足打記者","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:19:03.000Z","uid":86714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"68b3b718706e90e9017b00d20b9371ae67eb8c4e","tid":1468177,"uid":86714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:02:28.000Z","msg":"林鄭同中共一定會大造文章屈前線打採訪緊記者<br />\n如果開民間記者會<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要講清楚下面幾點</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢自己表示唔係記者</span></span><br />\n1. 佢宣稱係遊客<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 佢宣稱件記者衫係其他記者比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 佢冇法出示到記者證<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢行為同物品表示佢係鬼</span></span><br />\n1. 佢拎住I love 香港藍色tee，同上週末荃灣斬人嘅操普通話人士同一款<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 佢影人大頭，同鬼做嘅一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 佢見到人問佢唔對路就跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解要紥住佢</span></span><br />\n1. 基於週末著藍色tee嘅內地暴徒行為，你係唔會知佢幾時會郁手打人或者係褲袋變把刀出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"color: red;\">咁樣係以現場物資保護手足最安全方法</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點</span></span><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: blue;\">前線手足一如既往對傳媒朋友友好</span>。當時人多番表示唔係記者同證明唔係自己係記者，如果話手足阻礙採訪自由，實屬冤枉。<br />\n(e個一定要同公眾講)<br />\n<br />\n2. 一張證代表一個身份。<span style=\"color: red;\">當連環時果條友著人地件記者衫都話得自己係遊客，我地又點可以知道唔帶委任證嘅人係咪警犬?</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，決一不可</span>"},{"pid":"0e0f494812c40cc58a83feb363886fdfac8d96a9","tid":1468177,"uid":86714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:03:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df0633b38013096d9f32a58080c6b620ed7f3541","tid":1468177,"uid":86714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:04:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44c6688b0a7bfa555478f1d4d2824fce97ef1b76","tid":1468177,"uid":86714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd52384108897ae69af5a7e2b5942980470b3c8","tid":1468177,"uid":86714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9001e01f28d6ea5749e253467345279d194fc0","tid":1468177,"uid":86714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:06:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4392100b26118ddb51d30b8a7c9d9eb1c6f2bb1","tid":1468177,"uid":86714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2746778d54695ef3ccf08899744855fadcaf78","tid":1468177,"uid":86714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}